                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "For any non-integer magazine values the magazine size is simply rounded to the nearest whole number. For example, a Furis modded with a max rank Slip Magazine will have a calculated magazine size of 35 × (1 + 30%) = 45.5 , which will simply round to 45.5 ."
                }
